updates.content:
Vibe Music chale to dil khud hi gaane lage,
Har beat pe jazbaat apne rang dikhane lage.
Headphone laga, duniya ko thoda side kar de,
Vibe Music ke saath apni feeling ride kar le.

Life mein itna struggle zaroor karna,
Ki earphones ulajhne pe gussa nahi,
Bulki muskurahat aaye ki naya lene ka waqt hai! ğŸ˜‚ğŸ§

Aag woh nahi jo gharon ko jala de,

Bheed se alag nikalne ka dum rakhte hain,
Vibe humara sabse juda aur tez hai! ğŸ”¥ğŸ¦

Suron ki lehron par sapne behne lagte hain,

Har mood ka ilaaj hai yahan ke gaanon mein,
Vibe Music basa hai dil ke afsaanon mein. âœ¨
